---
title: Vegan Sweet Potato Coconut Curry Noodles with Green Beans, Peanuts & Lime
description: Web Description: A bright, flavorful coconut curry sauce makes these veggie-packed noodle bowls sing! You’ll simmer hearty sweet potatoes and green beans in that silky savory-sweet sauce, then toss in a tangle of springy lo mein noodles. Toasted peanuts add savory crunch while fresh cilantro and lime juice tie it all together!
